===Adnominal===
{{ja-pos|adnominal}}

# {{ja-def|彼の}} ''([[deictically]])'' [[that]] ... over there (far from the speaker and the addressee)
#: {{ja-usex|'''あの'''車は緑です。|'''あの''' くるま は みどり です。|'''That''' car '''over there''' is green.}}
# {{ja-def|彼の}} ''([[anaphorically]])'' [[that]] ... we both know (both the speaker and the addressee know)

